### 创建电站
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stationName": "深圳光伏电站A",
  "location": "广东省深圳市南山区",
  "capacity": 5000.00,
  "contactPerson": "张三",
  "contactPhone": "13800138000"
}

### 查询电站详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations/1

### 分页查询电站
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations?pageNum=1&pageSize=10

### 删除电站
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/stations/1
